<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] is slated to 
complete its withdrawal from the Gaza Strip by Wednesday [18 
May]. After the withdrawal and redeployment are completed, the 
IDF will hold a ceremony in the Qatif Bloc. Senior military 
sources told our military correspondent that the IDF is 
satisfied with the way in which the evacuation is proceeding. 
So far 1,500 Palestinian policemen arrived in the Gaza Strip, 
and a similar number is expected to arrive by Wednesday. 

