<F P=106> [Communique "No. 21" issued by the Ministry of Defense on 17 </F>
May; place not given] 
  [Text] 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih yesterday sent large numbers of 
barbaric forces with their vehicles into a deadly battle in a 
desperate attempt to break through the fortified defense of the 
Armed Forces. These forces, together with the masses of our 
people, are defending justice, freedom, and honor. This was 
preceded by false statements, such as those of al-Ansi and 
al-Iryani, that the barbaric forces advanced behind a human 
shield [words indistinct] into a deadly battle. 
  Our armed forces repulsed these forces by striking heavy 
blows on them on the fronts of al-Karish, Abyan, Qa'tabah, and 
Bayhan during which many of them surrendered, while the remnants 
(?fled) toward Qa'tabah, al-Rahidah, and al-Bayda with our 
forces still behind them. Our forces captured many arms and 
vehicles abandoned by the oppressors. 

</TEXT>

