<H3> <TI>   Salih Speaks to Saudi Monarch, UAE President </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Salih Speaks to Saudi Monarch, UAE President </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1805054794 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
0330 GMT 18 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1805054794 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A telephone conversation was held yesterday evening 
between Presidential Council Chairman Lieutenant General brother 
'Ali 'Abdallah Salih and his brother His Majesty King Fahad 
Bin-'Abd-al-'Aziz of Saudi Arabia and custodian of the two holy 
mosques. They talked about current developments in our country, 
issues of shared interest, and brotherly ties between the two 
brotherly countries. 
  Also yesterday evening, a telephone conversation was held 
between Presidential Council Chairman Lt. Gen. 'Ali 'Abdallah 
Salih and his brother His Highness Shaykh Zayid Bin-Sultan Al 
Nuhayyan, president of the brotherly United Arab Emirates [UAE]. 
They reviewed Yemeni developments and ties between the two 
brotherly countries. 

</TEXT>

