<H3> <TI>   ICRC Reaches Agreement on Care for War Captives </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ICRC Reaches Agreement on Care for War Captives </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA1505191194 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1700 GMT 15 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1505191194 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A statement issued by the Cairo office of the 
International Committee of the Red Cross [ICRC] says that the 
committee has reached agreements providing for visiting fighters 
detained by both sides in the dispute. The statement recalled 
that the committee had already visited a number of captives in 
Aden. It stressed that representatives of the Red Cross were 
continuing their efforts to supply medical organizations with 
basic supplies for the treatment of the war victims. 

</TEXT>

