<F P=100> ISRAEL </F>
<H3> <TI>   Peres Terms 'Arafat Remarks `Unfounded,' `Amazing' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Peres Terms 'Arafat Remarks `Unfounded,' `Amazing' </PHRASE></F></HT>

