BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres has termed unfounded 
the remarks 'Arafat made about a letter he had received from the 
Israeli Government regarding the future of Jerusalem. Minister 
Peres also said that 'Arafat's statement about the need to 
continue jihad is amazing and totally unacceptable. Israel will 
examine what exactly 'Arafat said and will respond in kind. 
Minister Peres made these remarks to our correspondent Shlomo 
Raz. 

</TEXT>

