<H3> <TI>   Al-Hirawi, al-Hariri Meeting Ends Cabinet Crisis </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Al-Hirawi, al-Hariri Meeting Ends Cabinet Crisis </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1705162294 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 17 May 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1705162294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Today's midday three-hour meeting between the two 
leaders, Ilyas al-Hirawi and Rafiq al-Hariri, at the 
presidential palace, has ended the governmental crisis that 
lasted one week. The meeting also ended talk of a reshuffle or 
change in government. This meeting took place after Prime 
Minister al-Hariri informed the cabinet yesterday during its 
extraordinary session that there will be no cabinet reshuffle. 

</TEXT>

