President to brag about opposing the U.S. war against Vietnam. 
He also has the right to say that he inherited the U.S. 
intervention in Somalia. He was the one who decided to withdraw 
U.S. troops from Somalia. Somali sacrifices and resolve also 
contributed to the withdrawal decision. 

