  [Text] Iraq has informed the Arab League that the Saudi and 
Kuwaiti rulers are continuing to provide facilities for U.S., 
British, and French aircraft to violate Iraqi airspace, which 
seriously threatens Iraq's security, sovereignty, and national 
unity. 
  In a letter he addressed yesterday to the Arab League 
