these attacks, in addition to the aforementioned losses, two 
rocket launchers, a DShKS, two PK machine-guns, and several 
militia strongholds were destroyed in the southeast of Kabul. 
  Recently, according to another report, 15 members of 
Dostam's 
militia sold their weapons in Charasiab in Kabul and fled to 
Pakistan via Kandahari bridge located in Mohammad Aqha District, 
Logar Province. [passage omitted] 

