<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A military statement issued by the Ministry of 
Defense mentioned that the assassin 'Ali 'Abdullah Salih plunged 
the day before yesterday big numbers of barbaric forces and 
quantities of his miltiary equipment in a desperate attempt to 
break through the fortified defense lines of our Armed Forces, 
standing with the masses of our people against the freedom and 
dignity [as heard]. This was preceded by false statements, such 
as the statements of al- Ansi and al-Iryani. And in front of 
these barbarous forces, from the helpless they presented human 
shields to the cemetery of death. The statement mentioned that 
our Armed Forces have come forward against taking shelter by the 
fighters in the cities and villages and making the citizens from 
the sons of our people human shields facing the weapons of 
destruction and killing. 
  We, in the name of the Yemeni people in every place, demand 
the immediate stopping of this foolish fighting, and we remind 
all that we are in the month of war-prohibition in the Hijriyyah 
[Islamic] calendar, in which almighty God prohibited fighting in 
them. We are even in the first 10 days of the month of 
Dhu'l-hijjah. What law except the law of the jungle allows 
this, and where are those insisting on fighting from Islam. It 
is rejected teaching and in Shari'ah, we in the name of the 
Yemeni people appeal to all Arab and Islamic countries and 
organizations to stand with us in calling on the fighters to 
cease fire, especially during the days of pilgrimage and the 
blessed 'Id al-Adha. 

</TEXT>

