<H3> <TI>   Shaykh Zayid Receives Salih's Envoy, Message </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shaykh Zayid Receives Salih's Envoy, Message </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1505101094 Abu Dhabi United Arab Emirates Radio Network in 
Arabic 0930 GMT 15 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1505101094 </F>
<F P=104>  Abu Dhabi United Arab Emirates Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] The President, His Highness Shaykh Zayid 
Bin-Sultan Al Nuhayyan, has received a message from His 
Excellency 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, chairman of the Yemeni 
Presidential Council, dealing with the latest developments in 
Yemen. The message was conveyed to the president by Yemeni 
Foreign Minister Muhammad Salim Basindwah who met with the 
president at the presidential office today. 
  President Zayid again called for an end to the internecine 
fighting and for preserving Yemen and the Yemeni people's 
achievements. He appealed to the Yemeni people to stop the 
bloodshed and seek the language of reason and dialogue to serve 
Yemen and its people. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

