<H3> <TI>   Amin Al-Hindi Arrives in Gaza Strip </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Amin Al-Hindi Arrives in Gaza Strip </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1905154694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1500 GMT 19 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1905154694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Amin al-Hindi, who was involved in planning the 
murder of Israeli athletes at the Munich Olympic Games in 1972, 
arrived in the Gaza Strip this afternoon through the Rafah 
border crossing. 
  Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that he was accompanied 
by his wife and several bodyguards. Al-Hindi is slated to be 
one of the commanders of the Palestinian security forces in the 
territories. Al-Hindi was in charge of security at the PLO 
offices in Tunis. 

</TEXT>

