  [Text] A communique has been issued by the security 
services, which says said that yesterday, 11 people, including 
eight policemen and three Russian nationals, were killed after 
an attack against a bus which was carrying Russians near the 
town of Ziama Mansouria in Jijel Province. The same source adds 
