marketing campaign and to facilitate procedures for receiving 
grains from peasants and farmers, a new marketing center for 
receiving grain in bulk and bags has been set up in Huwayjah 
District, in addition to increasing the absorption capacity of 
Tazah receiving center and adding scales to Zab marketing center. 

