President Saddam Husayn, may God prserve and protect him, who is 
always concerned about developing the agricultural sector and 
enhancing its resources and capabilities in order to ensure food 
for our brave Iraqi people and to defeat the unjust blockade on 
our struggler country. May God grant us success in serving our 
people under the builder of Iraq's glory leader President Saddam 
Husayn, may God preserve and protect him. 
